                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No.312.11/3047a.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">American Consular Officers in Mexico</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-12-26T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 26, 1913—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Prepare and transmit continuation to January 1, 1914, of report called for in
                    first paragraph of instruction of August 8th last.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">J. B. Moore</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
